column3: `iff` has special meaning in computer science: "[if and only if](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/If_and_only_if)". Not sure whether that meaning applies here but I presume it does.
I'm pretty sure this is not a typo.\nFWIW: This particular comment was added by @morcos in 2fffaa97381f741786fff2e6ff25f4b9a74037fe.\n
As above, I don't think it's a typo
